# Key Conventions

- Next.js 16 App Router, TypeScript strict, Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-first config)
- `@/` path alias for all imports
- Components are named exports, pages are default exports
- No em dashes in any writing. Use commas or periods.
- Editorial voice: direct, personal, concise. Not corporate.
- Dark-only theme (#0a0a0a background), 640px max width, minimalist design
- Color tokens defined in `app/globals.css` under `@theme inline`
- Static data lives inline in page files, not in separate data files
